<div class="container">
<h3><strong>Welcome to the Mercyhurst University Archives!</strong></h3>

<div class="hidden-xs hidden-sm">
<p>The University Collections contain a wealth of primary source material pertaining to important documents, institutional records, ephemera and realia about the University. The Ridge Collection contains material pertaining to important public policy matters covering Governor Ridge&#39;s time in office, along with extensive resources pertaining to First Lady Michele Ridge&#39;s commitment to and involvement with a number of important issues affecting the lives of Pennsylvanians.</p>
</div>

